B.qG=new A.cw("Unlocking Reliable Crash Tracking with PLCrashReporter for iOS SDKs","","https://youtu.be/18StJO-Acb8?si=juCmMnOhQJJBqoHU","In this pilot episode, me, Majid Hajian, Tom\xe1\u0161 Sk\xfdpala, and Tom\xe1\u0161 Soukal dive into the intricacies of mobile app security and crash tracking. The conversation revolves around Tom\xe1\u0161 Sk\xfdpala's insightful article for Talsec on developing transparent crash-tracking solutions for production.",null,null,!0)
