B.Ey=A.c(s(["Implemented an experimentation platform, enabling reliable A/B testing and precise user targeting, improving experiment turnaround time from weeks to hours.","Developed an in-house server-driven UI framework, empowering developers to introduce new features and fix issues post-release, reducing release cycles by up to 200%.",'Built a Web Simulator to replicate the mobile application on the web, facilitating internal feedback for experimental or "hard-to-reproduce" features.',"Implemented a mocked backend, enabling reliable integration testing.","Aligned production and staging environments to streamline incident investigation and resolution.","Contributed to Tide's engineering brand through public speaking and technical writing.","Introduced an innovative hiring approach, reducing recruitment time by 30% without compromising quality."]),t.s)
B.Ba=new A.e3("Engineering Manager","Tide","jun 2024","now","Leading the Experience Foundation team focusing on core functionalities driving mobile applications, experiments, and dev experience.",B.Ey)
B.DW=A.c(s(["Established and enforced security policies, including implementing RASP and anti-fraud measures to protect the banking platform.","Played a key role in migrating the mobile platform from native development to Flutter, creating a secure and scalable banking solution.","Provided technical guidance and expertise, ensuring the effective and efficient design of projects and systems.","Designed and maintained complex software architectures to ensure scalability, security, and maintainability.","Conducted code reviews to ensure adherence to best practices, design patterns, and coding standards.","Mentored and supported engineers, fostering skill development and career advancement.","Collaborated with cross-functional teams to align projects with strategic objectives.","Monitored emerging technologies and industry trends to identify potential applications within the organization.","Refined development processes, tools, and methodologies to boost productivity and software quality."]),t.s)
B.B9=new A.e3("Senior Staff Engineer","Tide","dec 2021","jun 2024","Shaping Tide's technical direction, fostering collaboration and technical excellence.",B.DW)
B.EI=A.c(s(["coordinate mobile tech.leaders and act as a consultant for mobile developers;","develop organizational policies and standards;","create quality targets and assure their appliance;","introduce new methodologies and tools, apply them on commercial projects;","act as a mobile stack expert during the sales process;","create learning programs, coordinate knowledge sharing activities;"]),t.s)
B.B6=new A.e3("Head of Mobile","Ciklum","april 2018","nov 2021","As a Head of Mobile Stack I:",B.EI)
B.DT=A.c(s(["I managed developers from iOS, Android, and cross-platform stacks. I owned the competence development process (assessment, education, certification, knowledge sharing, community development);","I responded for the alignment between personal development plans of each talent in the Mobile team with Ciklum's strategy;","Implemented a built-in quality approach across all mobile teams (including implementation of engineering practices, shared services, and technical audit process);"]),t.s)
B.Bd=new A.e3("Mobile Technical Lead","Ciklum","january 2017","april 2018","While still acting as a cross-platform mobile developer, I had more administrative activities.",B.DT)
B.Fx=A.c(s(["I developed cross-platform mobile applications in C#. Worked with F#, Objective-C, Swift, and Java. My target OS were iOS, Android, WP7, WP8, and UWP (Windows 10). Frameworks I used: Xamarin, Xamarin.Forms, FreshMvvm, Reactive Extensions, ReactiveProperty, RxUI, MvvmCross. I worked via TDD using NUnit, MSTest, and Moq. For a few projects used BDD with Calabash and Ruby. I acted as the chief reviewer during code reviews.","My primary responsibilities were team coaching and technical quality assurance. I improved and automated the internal processes: CI, metrics, workflows, and other best practices. I have conducted internal and external interviews.","I made estimations, participated in workshops, project, and proposal reviews. Supervised and participated in technology investigations and researches. Consulted client-side developers, responded for high-level architecture for projects."]),t.s)
B.B7=new A.e3("Xamarin Lead Dev","Ciklum","november 2012","december 2016","On this position, I was in charge not only for the software development but for the team.",B.Fx)
B.EK=A.c(s(["I started as a cross-platform mobile developer in C++ with the Marmalade SDK framework.","Soon I switched to C# and focused on young frameworks MonoTouch and MonoDroid, which became a foundation of the Xamarin platform afterward.","I developed a social network and a simple game for a brand new phone promotion."]),t.s)
